labels.value: This estimate is based upon the members eligibility and benefits as of the date the estimate is created. A statement of cost sharing liability for a covered item or service is not a guarantee that benefits will be provided for that item or service. The actual charges for a covered item or service may be different from the estimate of cost sharing liability provided, depending on the actual items or services you or your dependent receive at the point of care.

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 2
labels.value: The cost sharing estimate provided is only an estimate based on the items and services selected by the members. It does not include any additional , reasonably expected to be furnished services , and is subject to change; Please also keep in mind the following:

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 3
labels.value: If you or your dependents choose to see an out of network provider they may bill you for the difference between the provider's billed charges and the sum of the amount paid by your group health plan and the amount you paid in the form of a copayment or coinsurance amount (the difference referred to as balance billing), and that the cost sharing information provided above does not account for these potential additional amounts.

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 4

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 5

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 6
labels.value: This statement of cost sharing liability does not take into account any copayment assistance or other third-party payments in the calculation of your out-of-pocket maximum.

labels.shortDescription: Report Disclaimer part 7
